ubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-09/ty-article/.highlight/to-see-israels-moral-deterioration-since-october-7-just-turn-on-your-television/00000191-3272-de61-adb5-b27e20cc0000</guid></item><item><title>“之前我曾因为安全局势而放弃了以色列之行。我没有时间再等了&amp;#39;</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-08-08/ty-article/.highlight/i-passed-up-a-trip-to-israel-because-of-war-once-before-i-have-no-more-time-to-wait/00000191-3388-daa8-a3b7-f7dff71c0000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一对父子去朝圣，参观圣地并品尝 Shakshuka，一名匈牙利侨民向以色列的新移民传达了令人鼓舞的信息</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 20:18:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-08-08/ty-article/.highlight/i-passed-up-a-trip-to-israel-because-of-war-once-before-i-have-no-more-time-to-wait/00000191-3388-daa8-a3b7-f7dff71c0000</guid></item><item><title>“他们的头顶上没有屋顶”：数千名加沙人逃离汗尤尼斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/left-without-a-roof-over-their-heads-thousands-of-gazans-flee-khan-yunis/00000191-337c-d2d3-af9d-3ffdd2140000</link><description>以色列军队再次呼吁汗尤尼斯许多社区的居民前往马瓦西安全区。加沙紧急服务部门称，以色列周四袭击了舒贾耶两所学校，造成至少 15 人死亡，至少 30 人受伤</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 20:02:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/left-without-a-roof-over-their-heads-thousands-of-gazans-flee-khan-yunis/00000191-337c-d2d3-af9d-3ffdd2140000</guid></item><item><title>以色列废弃北部天空的观察者在真主党的无人机下创作艺术</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-08-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/watcher-of-the-skies-of-israels-abandoned-north-creates-art-under-hezbollahs-drones/00000191-32d5-dd83-a9bb-73df570d0000</link><description>在海法艺术博物馆，艺术家哈达尔·赛凡 (Hadar Saifan) 为一个孤独的地区发声。此外，一部纪录片讲述了诺瓦音乐节的悲惨故事，一本新书探讨了战时的女权主义</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 19:17:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-08-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/watcher-of-the-skies-of-israels-abandoned-north-creates-art-under-hezbollahs-drones/00000191-32d5-dd83-a9bb-73df570d0000</guid></item><item><title>阿拉伯世界在社交媒体上赞扬叶海亚·辛瓦尔登上哈马斯的最高宝座</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/on-x-arab-world-praises-sinwars-ascendancy-to-hamas-top-spot/00000191-31e4-d18b-a1b1-f3e7e1930000</link><description>随着长达10个月的加沙战争的持续，强硬派被认为是一个不错的选择，但一些评论家担心此举让这位10月7日建筑师有更大的许可与以色列“战斗到最后一个孩子”</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 18:43:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/on-x-arab-world-praises-sinwars-ascendancy-to-hamas-top-spot/00000191-31e4-d18b-a1b1-f3e7e1930000</guid></item><item><title>纳粹德国的犹太共产主义者、犹太复国主义者和反犹太复国主义者：艺术家莉亚·格伦迪格的一生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/jewish-communist-in-nazi-germany-zionist-and-anti-zionist-the-life-of-artist-lea-grundig/00000191-331d-d940-a991-f7df832c0000</link><description>在新兴以色列事业蓬勃发展的鼎盛时期，蜚声国际的犹太裔德国画家莉亚·格伦迪格 (Lea Grundig) 抛下一切回到了东德，在那里他的光芒逐渐褪去。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 18:43:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/jewish-communist-in-nazi-germany-zionist-and-anti-zionist-the-life-of-artist-lea-grundig/00000191-331d-d940-a991-f7df832c0000</guid></item><item><title>奇迹产业：10 月 7 日之后，谁会从超自然故事的扩散中受益？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/industry-of-miracles-who-benefits-from-the-supernatural-tales-proliferating-after-oct-7/00000191-326b-d2d3-af9d-3eff46940000</link><description>奈蒂沃特是否因三个正义之人出现在恐怖分子面前而免遭屠杀？ 10 月 7 日的破裂催生了数百个关于奇迹和救赎的故事，证明了需要从混乱中创造意义——当然还有一些人希望利用这种情况</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 17:48:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/industry-of-miracles-who-benefits-from-the-supernatural-tales-proliferating-after-oct-7/00000191-326b-d2d3-af9d-3eff46940000</guid></item><item><title>对于哈里斯来说，蒂姆·沃尔兹对以色列-巴勒斯坦冲突的沉默是一种财富</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/for-harris-tim-walzs-silence-on-the-israeli-palestinian-conflict-is-an-asset/00000191-315f-d3fe-adf5-397fce150000</link><description>卡马拉·哈里斯选择明尼苏达州州长蒂姆·沃尔兹作为副总统人选，这表明民主党明智地优先考虑反特朗普选民的注意力，而不是亲巴勒斯坦选民的注意力</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 15:34:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/for-harris-tim-walzs-silence-on-the-israeli-palestinian-conflict-is-an-asset/00000191-315f-d3fe-adf5-397fce150000</guid></item><item><title>敏感基地的以色列士兵如何透露他们的身份和位置</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldiers-at-sensitive-security-sites-reveal-their-identity-and-location-online/00000191-326a-d9ba-a5df-7a7b855a0000</link><description>《国土报》的一项调查：以色列国防军努力执行作战安全规定，尽管有关于智能手机和智能手表的明确指示，但敏感信息仍在泄露并很容易被敌人获取</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 15:07:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldiers-at-sensitive-security-sites-reveal-their-identity-and-location-online/00000191-326a-d9ba-a5df-7a7b855a0000</guid></item><item><title>尽管一再下令以色列警方不要没收反战抗议标语</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-continue-confiscating-anti-war-protest-signs-despite-repeated-orders-not-to/00000191-3249-dedb-abb7-7769e0ee0000</link><description>国家检察官办公室表示，禁止扣押政治标牌的命令已广泛传阅六次，但均被忽视</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 14:50:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-continue-confiscating-anti-war-protest-signs-despite-repeated-orders-not-to/00000191-3249-dedb-abb7-7769e0ee0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡告诉《时代》杂志，他对 10 月 7 日事件感到“抱歉”，现在“不是提出问责问题的时候”</title><link>https://www.