"true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-grants-citizenship-to-ugandan-jew-in-landmark-decision/00000191-2dd1-d1b4-a399-7df7ac820000</guid></item><item><title>高级官员表示，以色列警方不会调查极右翼暴徒袭击以色列国防军基地的事件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/police-arent-investigating-storming-of-idf-bases-by-far-right-mobs-senior-officer-says/00000191-3153-d4e2-a9dd-b37f214f0000</link><description>极右翼示威者闯入斯德泰曼和拜特利德的以色列军事基地，那里关押着涉嫌虐待巴勒斯坦被拘留者的以色列国防军士兵，一周半后，没有人受到讯问或逮捕——尽管冲突被媒体捕捉到。视频</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 10:22:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-08/ty-article/.premium/police-arent-investigating-storming-of-idf-bases-by-far-right-mobs-senior-officer-says/00000191-3153-d4e2-a9dd-b37f214f0000</guid></item></channel></rss>